\pard\f0\fs28 Glabrous, scapigerous annual. Sepals erect; petals white, sometimes absent; stamens 6, without appendages; ovary surrounded by a fleshy ring. Fruit a silicula; valves strongly convex. Seeds in 2 rows, 2-6 in each loculus.
